<section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="HA959B446B6FB415C99FDA5C53C837C19"><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">That the following named Members be, and are hereby, elected to the following standing committees of the House of Representatives:</text> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Agriculture:</header><text>Mr. Panetta.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Education and Labor:</header><text>Mr. Yarmuth, Mr. Espaillat.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> <committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Natural Resources:</header><text>Ms. McCollum, Mr. Cohen, Mr. Tonko, Ms. Tlaib. </text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header>Committee on Veterans’ Affairs:</header><text>Ms. Lois Frankel of Florida, Mr. Brown, Ms. Slotkin, Mr. Trone.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph> </section> </resolution-body> <attestation><attestation-group><attestor display="no">Cheryl L. Johnson,</attestor><role>Clerk.</role></attestation-group></attestation> </resolution> 

